            "text": "IN THE DESERT: WASTE MANAGEMENT PHOENIX OPEN",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Get ready to witness one of the most anticipated events in golf as the Waste Management Phoenix Open swings into action from February 8th to 11th! Held at the renowned TPC Scottsdale, this tournament isn't just about golf – it's a four-day celebration of sport, entertainment, and unrivaled fun.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
