        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Collaborations Launching During the Event",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In conjunction with the Waste Management Phoenix Open, two exciting collaborations are set to debut during the tournament. PUMA is unveiling the highly anticipated PUMA x PTC collection, featuring stylish and performance-driven apparel and accessories designed for the modern golfer. Created by Kygo and Rickie Fowler, this collection is casual meets performance, and perfect for on the golf course and off. Additionally, Travis Mathew is introducing its \"Wasted\" collection, offering a range of trendy and relaxed apparel perfect for both on and off the course. With these exclusive launches, attendees can elevate their style while embracing the spirit of the tournament.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
